{"tid":1203990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[立法會議員利申資料庫] - 石禮謙 !","createTime":"2019-06-11T14:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:02:13.000Z","uid":45741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fcfe593f31ad8e1b6bc4d9388bcbc203ee663c7","tid":1203990,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:00:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://app.legco.gov.hk/members-interests/chinese/members-interests.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.legco.gov.hk%2Fmembers-interests%2Fchinese%2Fmembers-interests.html&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=305564c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.legco.gov.hk/members-interests/chinese/members-interests.html</a><br />\n例如打石禮謙<br />\n就會搵到佢利申6月3號開始成為<br />\n遠東發展有限公司既獨立非執行董事 (受薪) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最睇多少少你會發現：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fecil.com.hk/tc/global/home.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fecil.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fglobal%2Fhome.php&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=8158f889\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fecil.com.hk/tc/global/home.php</a><br />\n石禮謙先生獲委任為<br />\n獨立非執行董事以及審核委員會、[<br />\nu]<strong>薪酬委員會</strong>[/u]及提名委員會各自之成員。<br />\n<br />\n石先生有權收取董事袍金<br />\n每年港幣220,000元，<ins><strong>有關薪酬經參考石先生於本公司之職務及職責以及當前市況後釐定。</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n而遠東發展有限公司係琴日(6月10號) 公佈<br />\n6月20日會舉行董事會會議<br />\n<ins><strong>6月20呢個日子咪下星期四？</strong></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6月20有咩特別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n純9up, 有錯請指教<br />\nLink: <br />\n<a href=\"http://doc.irasia.com/listco/hk/fareastcon/announcement/ca190531.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdoc.irasia.com%2Flistco%2Fhk%2Ffareastcon%2Fannouncement%2Fca190531.pdf&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=0a92da9d\" target=\"_blank\">http://doc.irasia.com/listco/hk/fareastcon/announcement/ca190531.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://doc.irasia.com/listco/hk/fareastcon/announcement/ca190610.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdoc.irasia.com%2Flistco%2Fhk%2Ffareastcon%2Fannouncement%2Fca190610.pdf&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=1105ec80\" target=\"_blank\">http://doc.irasia.com/listco/hk/fareastcon/announcement/ca190610.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://tinypic.com/r/sl5v1s/9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinypic.com%2Fr%2Fsl5v1s%2F9&h=a0956ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i63.tinypic.com/2pqkebr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi63.tinypic.com%2F2pqkebr.png&h=ea490009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cecafd9d5737f5a6eff8a69c4946a5b89712a0c1","tid":1203990,"uid":45741,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i65.tinypic.com/sl5v1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi65.tinypic.com%2Fsl5v1s.jpg&h=5331f60a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5ca947f1edfdf18002b90d2a0916a4039688311","tid":1203990,"uid":255494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0092f9b6fffaea9a81688e7a077382d38842772","tid":1203990,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}